Apache-Syntax-Highlight-Perl version 1.01
=========================================

This package is a mod_perl (1.0 and 2.0) module that provides syntax
highlighting for Perl code. This module is a wrapper around
Syntax::Highlight::Perl.

See perldoc Apache::Syntax::Highlight::Perl for module documentation and use

CHANGES FROM PREVIOUS VERSION

	- Fixs documentation bugs [thanks to Ken Burcham <ken@burcham.com>]
	
See 'Changes' file in this distribution for complete history revision

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   o mod_perl 1 or 2 (of course)
   o Syntax::Highlight::Perl >= 1.00

